## âš™ï¸ How to Use

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Tommy813-lab/Terraform-EC2-Auto-Deploy.git

2. Customize variables in terraform.tfvars


3. Initialize and apply:

terraform init
terraform apply


4. SSH into the instance:

ssh -i key.pem ec2-user@<public-ip>



