### ğŸ”¹ 3. **Terraform â€“ No Hardcoding**

Replace this:
```hcl
ami = "ami-08c40ec9ead489470"
instance_type = "t2.micro"

With:

variable "ami_id" {}
variable "instance_type" {
  default = "t2.micro"
}

Then put this in terraform.tfvars:

ami_id        = "ami-08c40ec9ead489470"
instance_type = "t2.micro"
